                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Près de la porte Saint-Martin,\nPassant la veille du scrutin,\nJ’vis un homm’ qui collait à plat"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Je m’approche, en disant comm’ça :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Les candidats, ma foi, j’m’en fiche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Mais’y a du bon sur cette affiche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Votons pour ce citoyen-là !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je m’approche, en disant comm’ça :\nLes candidats, ma foi, j’m’en fiche,\nMais’y a du bon sur cette affiche,\nVotons pour ce citoyen-là !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Un autre homme arrive soudain,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
