                    "line_text": "Un grand pot de colle à la main,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Sur le mur, il coll’ tranquill'ment",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un autre homme arrive soudain,\nUn grand pot de colle à la main,\nSur le mur, il coll’ tranquill'ment"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Je lis le morceau tout entier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Pas fâché d’êt’ fixé tout d’même,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Je m’dis : Votons pour le deuxième,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Il promet plus d’chos’ que l’premier !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je lis le morceau tout entier,\nPas fâché d’êt’ fixé tout d’même,\nJe m’dis : Votons pour le deuxième,\nIl promet plus d’chos’ que l’premier !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
